column1: my handsome little man 💕 my thumbs hurt so bad from hook griping but then black d made a come back with suga shane! 💪😁 15.4 tested me mentally today. don't ask if you don't want to hear the truth hate dressing up for stuff especially when i don't even wanna go is this real life? love you 💕 marina knows me so well i can't tell if sushi counts as a cheat meal? can't wait for chris young this year 😍🙌 i just want warm weather so i can start doing swimming wods 😈😁 too excited for a thin mint protein shake & my cheat meal tomorrow. thanks dave 😍🙌 but we can pick a different workout i still have it haha! & scratch the diane idea! i'm doing the open sunday 15.4 hell yeah! 😈 hand stand push-ups! practice! or do the scalded version off the box! you should know this tony! it's 21-15-9 of deadlifts and hspu diane duh lmao oh! i was just going to add in dubs and ghds  what the hell tony! fineeeeee i'll wait! but i get a 20 sec head start get ready for diane today...with a twist 😈 "you want them when they don't want you, soon as they do feelings change." feelings haven't changed sleep, protein shakes, squats, & coffee are my favorite 😍 i could listen to his voice over & over 😌 noah ohlsen is such a babe 😍 well you need to start because i bought you a pretty cork! rt happy paddy's day everyone!! raise that good shit high with your finest paddy's worldwide!! #eire!! don't ask me to go out for a drink and not invite your girlfriend along 😂 #scum were doing arm bars today at crossfit? please tell me it's actual mma 😍 rt ladies if you have a flat ass omg two rest days in a row is too long 😫 i just wanna lift crying right now 😍 join the club! practice what you preach i'm not one to ever complain about eating a lot but....damn when your coach ups your protein intake 😳 much needed rest day today. my neck feels so much better! so true rt do people actually enjoy taking baths or do they want to post something on instagram so they buy a bath bomb and take … i hate getting hurt more than anything! it's such a set back at least i don't have the anxiety watching the fights !! rt bigg rigg is back! dominating performance by #ufc185 i'm missing the fights tonight and no where in worcester has them on! wtf i think she's drunk why are my hip piercing getting caught on my pants 😡 a little ja rule to start the night i need my shoulder massaged in the worst way 😫 i can't move my neck! haha i should have listen to you and had one more! it's so weird driving in a car compared to my   rt tbh i rather have all this rain than snow☔️ i could use a beer or 10 🍻 this is so true sushi 😍 only thing making my shoulder feel a little bit better and i had a donut because i'm sad now 😭 if this screws me up for 15.3 i will seriously cry and this is what i get for working my shoulders almost everyday this week rt if she's a  er she's a keeper. almost went into the shower with my socks on rt pettis vs dos anjos!!! rt hendricks vs brown!!! rt you're an addict one is cinnamon toast crunch and another is like reese puffs...how could i say no 😳 can never have enough options i spend so much money at psn & i'm not even mad about it 😍 love it & yeeeeww! but you more 😘💕 15.3 🔫 yet as soon as they ask me for a favor i drop everything to help them out i hate when people say that they will do something for you but never follow through with it omg you're killing me 😫😭 and you're not sharing?! 😡😤 aw nooooo 😫 feel better 😘😘💕 just saw driving 💕 but why so serious? haven't had an iced coffee in so long 😍 and have a nice ass 💁 i'm pretty sure i hit every pothole on my way home 😑🔫 cause we're like fire & gasoline, i'm no good for you, you're no good for me i love under estimating myself 😄 nope keep 😳🔫 keep owner for life ❤️ i just confused as to why your sending me random selfies? does metal mulisha mean more than one thing? because this guys truck is decked out in decals for it...#mmajunkie got all the way home and then a throwback usher song came on 😍🙌 took a little detour grabbed a shaker bottle without the ball.... cadbury mini eggs are my weakness 😫 people that do cardio for fun...wtf is wrong with you?! give me weights any day rt i'll never buy shoes for 100 dollars or more unless they are for training i just wanna take your time this time change is really hitting me today 😴 i need a vacation the weekend goes by too quick tried to buy stuff from rogue...too bad i maxed out my credit card again 😭🙈 i haven't been to a regular gym in over 2 years & i don't know why i want to go to one lately can't have your cake & eat it too 💁 any girl can look good with a pound of foundation & a good filter drove all the way to the packy, not even for myself, & forgot my id 😑 my life extra cardio 🔫 this weather is more confusing than the mind of a woman hate jerking, but i prd my split jerk! 😁💪 rt and this is me everyday 2nd cheat meal this weekend 🙈 but bella's is always worth it! my brother just bought another new car 😑 kid has his own house too. stop being the good child i love this, her, and that movie wooo! i just want to go to reebok just ate my body weight in flipz and mini cadbury eggs 💁 breaking my back just to know your name and now they are talking about relationships 🔫🔫🔫🔫🔫🔫🔫 mackenzie thought i ordered a "black guy chai"...i ordered a black eye chai 😂 & are talking about basketball... idk what the hell they are talking about 😒 seriously though, it doesn't take longer than a half hour to change my oil 😡 as much as i didn't want to get my oil changed today, i think i just found my soulmate beard mate 😍 just bought cinnamon toast crunch flavored protein powder! 😍 i meant in general! why am i taking a rest day on a friday when i get out of work at 12 and literally could spend my whole day working out 😫😭 sure for 15.2 lets redo 14.2. let's not and say we did 😡 efffff you chest to bar pull ups 😭 i'm just glad i'm getting sushi tomorrow 😍 hell yeah i'm pumped! 💪😁 bring on 15.2 rt let me love you by mario is sucha panty dropper pretty darn close lol honestly couldn't even tell you lmao me and alcohol aren't really friends right now, so i'll stick to soaking it real good lol rt should prob just toss it that thing is probably toxic by now risked my life and smelt it, still smells like my peanut butter protein! it's good! so happy i don't have my chest dermal piercings anymore found a protein shaker in the back of my car....i'm terrified to open it 😳 it's definitely not shorts and t-shirt weather buddy rt cybory's manager: she will compete one more time at 145 lbs, aim for 135 lbs after that, then hopefully rousey by year's e… know yourself, know your worth i can honestly say this is the happiest i've ever been sitting right now is a struggle 😣 #holysquats too bad it's not though how it should be take me to bella's, to get sushi, and lift more than me. it's that simple pr on my front squat tonight & my parents brought me home some bella's 😍 i can only imagine 😳 my knee is going to looooove max effort front squats today 😈🔫 but my text is more important than this is dark gray on light gray acceptable? you still kicked ass! 💪😁 i'm sure this will change by wednesday, but i'm honestly impressed with myself! ☺️ rt anyone can win my heart with a family size box of cheezits and/or ranch wheat thins sounds like a plan stan! we can swap it haha! & go to open gym thursday & we can do that one! the rings are close to the ground and you lay down and bring your chest to the rings 👌 dun dun duuuuuun yes! but i changed k2e to ring rows the dirty 30 & a bunch of dubs! i'm finding so many workouts for us to do 😈 almost forgot my carb in my meal. who am i?! 😳 rt im already so excited 2 hour lunches on mondays 👌 i'm obsessed with my back muscles 😍 ronda rousey is absolutely gorgeous 😍 rt my mom had a whole bottle of wine...she's dwunk 😂🙈 supermodel documentary hour "how often do you shave your hands?" just your typical crossfit conversation 😂 so glad i didn't get the fights last night. $50 would have been wasted on a 14 second fight cleaned 135# twice but couldn't get the jerk 💁 at least 15.1 & 15.1a are done 🙌 clean & jerk 125# woooo! i'm in no mood to do 15.1 & 15.1a today they're that cheap there?! i wish i knew 😫 but we went to mai tais in worcester we love you more 😘 mai tais will catch up to you jones vs rumble!!!! 😳 #ufc187 the hangover after the first hangover that never really went away 😫😭 getting a massage when you're hungover is one of the best things i've ever done when i take my shirt off when i work out that's when you know i'm serious.....ly pissed off i wore a long sleeve shirt 😡 can't wait for mai tais tonight 😍🍹 noah ohlsen 👌 this girl 😂 i love her & so happy she's a part of the family and we ain't gotta tell nobody, we ain't gotta tell nobody life goals nothing comes easy, if you want it then you have to work for it. his voice is amazing "where are your calves?" "your legs are about as flat as my chest!" 😂😂😂😭😭😭 it is what it is oh hahaa! i thought you knew wait, guys still wear pants tighter than yoga pants?! 😳 5 hours of sleep is not enough for this old lady rt #tweetyourlifeinapicture then i could be an octagon girl livin' the dream life i just want to be back in vegas falling asleep right now would be nice fool me once shame on me, fool me twice shame on me. 💁 don't be a fool in the first place, but we all have to learn somehow. lmao! 😭😂 i need to see this again. with wine & chocolate you got it 👌 i love cleaning 💪😍 #realbitchesclean the only 2 things i look forward to in my day is the gym & going home to my bby 🐶 my mom is literally my ride or die 💕 i can't wait for my massage mini heart attack 😳 bitches getting caught up with man ✋ everyone gets caught up ❄️⛄️🔫 drinking like the pros ☕️ everyone is always stressing about relationships 😂 relax people
